===[[Pokémon Masters EX]]===
{{main|Calem (Masters)}}
Calem, who is based on the [[rival]], forms a [[sync pair]] with {{p|Espurr}} and its evolved form {{p|Meowstic}}, along with {{Shiny}} {{p|Greninja}}, {{p|Fennekin}}, and {{p|Sylveon}} in [[Pokémon Masters EX]]. Calem joins the {{player}} after completing the twentieth chapter of the [[PML arc]].

Calem has also made notable appearances in the game's main stories: the PML arc, [[Legendary Adventures]], and the [[villain arc]].

